{"tid":1461822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有航班取消！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T09:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:13:05.000Z","uid":21202,"like":55,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"d0be1198daf2731f26e9e4bf1f0708caafa57a78","tid":1461822,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:23:50.000Z","msg":"現場聽到 一手資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c99f95c070a0a72c21ebe528a7651e24470763a","tid":1461822,"uid":237893,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:24:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警畜出沒注意</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警畜出沒注意</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警畜出沒注意</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請留意帶頭搞事嘅人 極有可能係警畜！<br />\n有需要嘅影低佢地嘅裝束，方便冷氣軍師研究！"},{"pid":"c7fbc2d5ec1f964886d39db1ecdf82eb8dcf589d","tid":1461822,"uid":52804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:24:40.000Z","msg":"FC未"},{"pid":"ccec5f385a470d4f08310e8b838e521d4e8aa104","tid":1461822,"uid":165925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:24:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n部分黑警察停止濫用武力<br />\n部分示威者停止暴力衝擊<br />\n政府作出讓步並不再企硬<br />\n歡迎和理非繼續<span style=\"color: pink;\">合法</span>示威</span></span><br />\n<br />\n齊上齊落同時請考慮每個行動既利與弊<br />\n否則恐怕變成文革2.0<br />\n目標稍有雜質 <br />\n大家就骨牌效應集體做偏左<br />\n花你搭車痾屎時間去重溫<br />\n鏗鏘集：文革五十年（上）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZOqrQnxq0jA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZOqrQnxq0jA&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDbxvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=58e61577\" target=\"_blank\">https://yout